e":"2019-09-22T21:51:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ed7c84b3a2c864d30a573e281b59d556cf44055","tid":1588326,"uid":127618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T00:35:58.000Z","msg":"唔好再太聚焦黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a0ee505fdfdd6b272e0f5f9d93205235ff73e63","tid":1588326,"uid":76435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T00:38:38.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n政府要解決問題 就要有真普選"},{"pid":"f79eb35ae696cdceea4a17a2812e1882ce487cf3","tid":1588326,"uid":228337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T00:42:23.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n<br />\n我覺得我哋要叫下新口號<br />\n關注更多雙普選&amp;解散警隊 <br />\n<br />\n雖然我都想黑警死全家<br />\n但發洩情緒的話，唱歌都夠（？）"},{"pid":"1995f6d372578e307ec85726f27ee3efbd11dcd5","tid":1588326,"uid":318070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T00:48:19.000Z","msg":"當你追緊monster時，別讓自己成為monster"}]}